devdoc.details: Contract to manage a list of approved music records and allow users to add them to their favorites

addRecord(string).details: Adds an approved record to the user's favorites

params._albumName: The name of the album to be added

constructor.details: Constructor that initializes the approved records list

getApprovedRecords().details: Returns the list of approved records

returns._0: An array of approved record names

getUserFavorites(address).details: Returns the list of a user's favorite records

returns._0: An array of user's favorite record names

resetUserFavorites().details: Resets the caller's list of favorite records
